    "body": "@sethrj requested the ability to add virtual packages to environments using `spack add`.\r\n\r\nThis PR allows virtual packages to be added to the `specs` list using the `add` command.\r\n\r\nVirtual packages are already allowed in named lists in spack environments/stacks.\r\n\r\nVirtual packages are already allowed in the `specs` list when added using the yaml directly.",
